This .spec file and corresponding downloader will help you to build a Qt 5 RPM.

The basic commands are:
 ./download.sh 5.5.0-alpha1
 rpmbuild --define 'qtversion 5.5.0' --define 'qtsuffix -alpha1' qt.spec

 To change the architecture, pass
 --define '_arch armhf'

 To give qbs arguments, pass
 --define 'arguments "profile:buildroot"'
